<h2 id="chords-needed">Chords needed</h2>

<p>The entire song uses a F-Am progression (with a D-minor thrown in a few times as a transitional chord).</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Barre chords:            Slightly simplified:

